name: John T. Rose 🥀
bio:
Entertainment Attorney @foxrothschild
Label Executive @collectivegllry
Featured in @forbes, @billboard, @variety, @hollywoodreporter & more #DREAMBIG

social_posts.post_text: Thanking God everyday that I made it and we still climbing! Special shout to @variety for acknowledging my partner and mentor @leronrogers and myself as a 2022 Top Dealmaker in the nation. As the youngest person in the room, I never take any of these moments for granted. Next year will be even bigger. #DreamBig 🥀

Overdue but right on time! Congratulations @bankheadprod on your platinum plaque and Billboard #1 accomplishment! Shout out to my day 1 sister and super manager @niiiniii as well. Whole team winning. #DreamBig 🥀
Moments like this make it all worth it.  Congratulations @kenyavaun on your new journey with @300ent !! Time to show the world everything you got!! #DreamBig 🥀

Ink dry and another deal wrapped up. Congratulations @sircharles1 on your first major publishing deal!! We always knew your hard work would pay off. Special shout out to my family @sammye_scott and @kdalmg for bringing this home. #DreamBig 🥀
Life is a beautiful thing once you stand behind the decisions you’ve made. 100 plaques and counting. Who else dreaming chasing this year? #DreamBig 🥀
Grammy Week 2023. Let’s bring home some hardware!! #DreamBig 🥀
Congratulations to our clients on their nominations and wins tonight. God is the greatest. #DreamBig 🥀
Another one in the books. Congratulations to our client @mehganjames on her new deal with @artistpg | Only great things to come!! #DreamBig 🥀
Dreaming Big, Defeating The Odds. Super Lawyers Rising Stars list two years in a row. #DreamBig 🥀

Thank you Georgia State University College of Law for having me as a guest speaker on the “A Day in the Life of an Entertainment Lawyer” panel discussion. Over 50 speaking engagements and these moments still feel unreal. #DreamBig 🥀

social_posts.post_text: Influencing change in our community one step at a time. This year’s Love Honor & Respect Teen Empowerment Conference was nothing short of amazing!! It was our first in person conference post the pandemic and we had a full house. Thank you to all of our sponsors, speakers, vendors, volunteers and partners that made this event happen!! Special shout out to the teenagers that showed up to the event ready to learn and empower themselves!! This is only the beginning. #DreamBig 🥀

text_entities.entity: love honor & respect teen empowerment conference

social_posts.post_text: My sister from day one!!! Always trusted the process and stayed true to yourself. I love and couldn’t be more proud of you. Congratulations @ladylondon on your major label deal with @defjam !! Time to run it up!!! #DreamBig 🥀

Music is a beautiful form of art and expression that must be protected. Thank you to the University of Pennsylvania Law School for having me as a guest speaker on your “A Poetic Injustice: Rap Lyrics in Criminal Prosecutions” panel discussion. #DreamBig 🥀
Never give up on the lifestyle you promised yourself. Still dream chasing. #DreamBig 🥀

Thank you Emory School of Law and the Center for Transactional Law and Practice for having me as a Keynote Speaker at this year’s graduation ceremony. Truly a full circle moment that I don’t take for granted. To the 2023 graduates, congratulations again on all of your accomplishments. I look forward to seeing you across the deal table. #DreamBig 🥀

text_entities.entity: center for transactional law and practice

social_posts.post_text: Who would have thought a young black boy from Southside Jamaica Queens NY would have a documentary with one of the largest lifestyle brands in the world. Thank you to @theathletesfootusa for the opportunity, recognition and work you guys are doing with the “How I Got my StAART” series pouring into the community. Still dream chasing. Full video in bio. #DreamBig 🥀

Words cannot express how proud we are of @cocojones and her many accomplishments!! From your Billboard #1 charting record, to your first RIAA Gold Certification and now Best New Artist at the 2023 BET Awards. This is only the beginning and you deserve everything God has in order for you. Congrats to the entire team here!! #DreamBig 🥀
Congrats are in order!! Huge shout out to our client @kaliii on her two new RIAA certifications and congrats to the entire team for all your hard work. Many more wins to come. #DreamBig 🥀

Extremely excited to be part of history!! Thank you @leronrogers for allowing me to work under your guidance. Thank you @warnerchappellmusic in believing in the vision. And finally, thank you @kaliii for trusting us and allowing us to be on your team. This is only the beginning. #DreamBig 🥀

location.city_name: Georgia State University College of Law

social_posts.post_text: Had the pleasure of speaking as a guest professor on the “Legal Life of Rick Ross” course being taught for the first time ever at Georgia State Law School. As a young attorney, it’s beyond a blessing to learn and play a small role in the boss’s historic legacy. Thank you @leronrogers and @ydavila for paving the way and huge shout out to professor @moivoryshow for changing the law school experience as we know it. #DreamBig #RoadToABillion 🥀
Nothing worth having comes easy. #MoreLife #DreamBig 🥀🎊
Time flies. You define your own life. Always grateful for the opportunities. #DreamBig 🥀

Excited to be speaking as a panelist to our next generation of future leaders during this year’s #BlackAndUnlimited HBCU Tour!! Amazing conversation during our first stop @centralstate87 | Thank you @Revolttv and @Walmart for the opportunity!!! #Walmart #WalmartPartner #DreamBig 🥀
Second stop on the #BlackAndUnlimited HBCU Tour powered by @walmart and @revolttv in the books! Thank you @officialvsutrojans for having us!! #Walmart #WalmartPartner #DreamBig 🥀

What a journey this has been. Stop 3 on the #BlackAndUnlimited HBCU Tour powered by @walmart and @revolttv was nothing short of amazing. Thank you @nccueagle for having us and to everyone in attendance!! #Walmart #WalmartPartner #DreamBig 🥀

Final stop @mvsu1950 for the #BlackAndUnlimited HBCU Tour. Sooner or later, your work speaks for itself. Thank you again to @walmart and @revolttv for the life changing opportunity. #Walmart #WalmartPartner #DreamBig 🥀
Congratulations @bankheadprod on your worldwide publishing deal with @ultrapublishing !! You deserve it. Shout out to @niiiniii and the entire team for making this happen. #DreamBig 🥀
God is the greatest. Thank you @emoryuniversity for the recognition. Attending @emorylaw changed my life and I look forward to paving the way for the next generation of attorneys to come. #DreamBig 🥀
